title: Bisa Masak
description: BisaMasak application is a gamification-based cooking recipe application designed to provide a more interactive and engaging cooking experience for users. The app provides recipes that can be customized to the user's skill level, as well as an ingredient search feature that helps find recipes based on ingredients available at home.
